WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:04.766
What is this?

2
00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:06.366
Just look at it

3
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.200
Kidney transplant surgery

4
00:00:15.733 --> 00:00:17.866
You mean to take my own kidney

5
00:00:17.866 --> 00:00:19.000
For your son

6
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.266
It's not a gift, it's a compensation.

7
00:00:21.266 --> 00:00:23.200
This is what you owe Xiaohui

8
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:26.600
No no no no

9
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.300
I can't die yet

10
00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:30.166
I didn't say I was going to die.

11
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:31.466
I have to save my mom

12
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:33.100
I promised my mom

13
00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:35.500
I want to live well with him

14
00:00:35.933 --> 00:00:37.433
You can't die.

15
00:00:37.466 --> 00:00:39.433
Can my son die?

16
00:00:40.333 --> 00:00:42.066
Zihui is my heart

17
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:44.400
Is the future heir to the Su family

18
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:47.166
Those who want to come out of the countryside are also crushed

19
00:00:47.566 --> 00:00:49.966
Use your kidney to save the turtle's life

20
00:00:49.966 --> 00:00:51.966
It is the blessing you have cultivated in eight lifetimes.

21
00:00:52.366 --> 00:00:54.100
No no

22
00:00:54.533 --> 00:00:56.666
Didn't you just say you have to take responsibility?

23
00:00:56.666 --> 00:00:59.100
Didn't you say you can help with anything?

24
00:00:59.300 --> 00:01:01.100
It's just a kidney.

25
00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:02.566
I also left you one.

26
00:01:02.566 --> 00:01:04.900
We have done our best to you.

27
00:01:04.966 --> 00:01:09.100
But I only have one now

